Relational database service
uses sql language
allows to create db in cloud managed by aws
Storage backed by EBS
BUT you cant SSH into your instances

RDS DEPLOYMENTS:
READ REPLICAS: for read scalabilitY
  can create upto 15 read replicas
  data is only written to main db

MULTI-AZ
  failover in case of AZ outage
  can have only 1 other az as failover
MULTI-REGION
  in different regions
  disaster recovery
  local performance for global reads
  replication cost!
